UID:0Zt7WYAbqGFQkR4hh7gS0
SUMMARY:Artist Talk: Wrapped in Memory with Job García
DTSTAMP:20260627T100811Z
DTSTART:20260627T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Houston Public Library on Saturday\, June 27th\,
	 from 2 - 4 PM for a partnered artist talk with Job García on his forthcom
	ing photo book ¡Qué Vivan las Cobijas\, Cabrones! Family Artifacts and the
	 Maintenance of Mexican Identity! Moderated by Areli Navarro Magallón\, Ex
	hibitions & Programs Coordinator at HCP.\n\nhttps://www.edu.hcponline.org/
