DESCRIPTION:Join us every Thursday for hands-on gardening projects at the J
	apanese Garden. From 9 a.m. to 12 p.m.\, come help with seasonal tasks lik
	e planting\, weeding\, mulching\, and pruning. A great way to connect with
	 others and make a visible impact in the Park! \nNo experience needed. All
	 ages are welcome. \nClick here to sign up!\n\nhttps://hermannpark.org/eve
	nt/japanese-garden-volunteer-day-6/\n\nFrom Hermann Park Conservancy
